While at the TeachScheme! 2005 summer workshop, I noticed that some of the menu items, specifically in the "Scheme" menu, do not have mnemonics or have duplicate mnemonics.  Both "Comment Out..." options use the letter C, adding an extra keystroke or two to select an item.
